title: #327 Wranglin' Man
description:
Holy Hell, after apologizing for Joe's fucked up mic (which we fixed, duh), Mark lets us in on his glock-carrying store clerk filled trip to Nawlins' before he bombs some charity gigs, while Joe races a Nor'easter from Boston to Cleveland. Check it out!
